def: A projection in a building; also, a pier or mole; a jetty.Shak.
The quality or state of being superabundant; a superabundantquantity; redundancy; excess.
Of, pertaining to, or having a character of, a minim orminimum; least; smallest; as, a minimal amount or value.
To inhere or exist together, as in one substance. Sir W.Hamilton.
Inclined to remit punishment; lenient; clement. Drayton.
